    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris, Filii et Spiritu Sancti. Anno dominice nativita[tis]
                        mill[esimo] centesimo nono, <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/52"
                            >Pascalis</persName> in apostolatu anno hoctavo, reg[n]a[nte] Carlo anno
                        tercio, die vieximo quarto mensis iulius, indictione secunda, in <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/80">Ferrarie</placeName>. Petimus ad
                        vos domnus <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Teobaldus Pomposianus"
                                >Tebaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> et domno <persName key="#Monks">
                            <name ref="Petrus Pomposianus">Petrus</name></persName> monachus, pro in
                        vicem ex persona dompno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4306"
                            >Litefredo</persName> gracia Dei habas de <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monesterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Exenia #Land_clearing #Canals #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Districtio #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancta Maria in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, uti nobis
                        presentibus <persName><name ref="Paulus Carantanus">Paulo
                            Carantano</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Petrus Buthrellus"
                                >Petrus Buthrello</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Hubertus">Uberto</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Bona">Bona</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Ermengarda">Mengarda</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Cazana">Cazana</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus Russo">Petrus Russo</name></persName> pro
                                <persName><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName> nebcia mea
                        ********** et <persName><name ref="Dominicus Menclellus">Dominicus
                                Menclello</name></persName>, pro nobis et pro aliis nostris
                        confratribus, secundum inter nos ist dividere debetis nostrisque filiis et
                        heredibus, in annis venihentibus viginti novem, itest omnes rex sortes et
                        porciones in integras quantascunque nos prescriptis petitoribus et petitrice
                        tenere et laborare visi estis ad iure monesterio Sancta Maria in Pomposia
                        per hanteriore libellum infra totam <rs key="#Plebs">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3660">Sancta Maria qui vocatur
                            in <placeName ref="#places/3546">Gab[ia]na</placeName></orgName>, ipsa
                        rem qui est in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Exenia #Land_clearing #Canals #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/4839">Mulsatam</placeName>: da primo capite firmante usque
                        in <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">valle</rs> que est iusta llatere
                        iuris <orgName key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Confinia"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3661">Sancti Stefani qui vocatur in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4840">Vicovencia</placeName></orgName>, secundo llatere
                        firmante usque in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers #Confinia" ref="#places/3546">Gabi[ana]</placeName>
                        percurrente, seu a tercio llatere possidet ********** adque a quarto llatere
                        possidet h[ere]des quondam <persName key="#Confinia"><name
                                ref="Petrus de Gregorio">Petrus de Gregorius</name></persName>. Que
                        omnia cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs> seu <rs key="#Casalia"
                            >casalibus</rs>, <rs key="#Canals">fosis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pasculis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs>salecti</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscacionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >capellacionibus</rs> vel omnibus ad prescripta rex pertinentibus in
                        integrum, instituto <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2410">Ferrariensi</geogName>. Hec
                        cedimus nobis habendum, tenendum, possidendum, laborandum, cultandum,
                        suprasedendum, laborandum, defensandum, meliorandum, prescripti viginti
                        novem annis venihentibus expletis, salve et iuste domnicum dandum, alia
                        libelli pagina in oc hordine renovemur. Ut inferratis quidem cum nostris
                        filiis et heredibus nobis nostrisque successoribus annualiter <rs
                            key="#Levies">terraticum</rs> de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">sicale</rs> in campo capa quarta, trahendas
                        ad area tritulata per vos petitores, de <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> in area
                        sestareum quartum, <rs key="#Cereals">mesturea ingranata</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Cereals">ordeata</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">trisico</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">milio</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                            >panico</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">cetero minuto</rs> in area
                        sestareum sestum, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> manna sesta, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vino</rs> anfora tercia, semel une arbore pecto ponendo, postea sit
                        nobis concessum; vinea si extra casale plantaveritis, post in torta venerit,
                        frui debetis annis novem, postea recdetis terraticum sicut superius legitur;
                        et si <rs key="#Land_clearing">roncaveritis</rs> frui debetis annis trex,
                        postea rendere debeatis sicut de cetera terra; <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs>
                        vero annualiter dare debeatis pro casale denarei duodecim de monete
                        Veneticorum tantum, deductum ipsum terratico domnico per nos petitores usque
                        ad mansione vestra domnica hic in civitate Ferrarie. Maiore quidem domnico
                        vestro vel vestra dominacione cum honore et hobedihencia suscipere debeatis,
                        nec liceat nobis de ac re ad <rs key="#Districtio">nullum placitum ire</rs>
                        nisi ante vos et ante vestros heredes conceditore vel successores. Si qua
                        vero pars vestrorum contra hanc libelli paginam iverit vel si omnia sicut
                        supra legitur non conservaverit, det pars parti fidem servanti, pene nomine,
                            <rs key="#Penalty">auri uncias duas</rs> et soluta pena in sua stet
                        firmitate. Quam scribere rogavimus <persName key="#Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellionem</rs> et manu vestra firmavimus in die et
                        indictione prescripta. Ego Litefred(us) abbas s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
